short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Saves the classes to use in the Random Team Generator for randomlists.org.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows you to make groups and store them in the synced storage on your Google Account. You can use these groups on randomlists.org's Random Team Generator to generate random groups effortlessly!
